==================================================
POST-MVP EXPANSION LAYER
COMPETITIVE INTELLIGENCE & WIN PROBABILITY ENGINE
==================================================

PURPOSE:
The platform must evolve beyond:
- contract discovery
- opportunity qualification
- execution planning

The platform should analyze:
- who actually wins contracts
- why they win
- what patterns exist
- what pricing ranges succeed
- what maturity level is required
- what competition exists
- whether the user can realistically compete

==================================================
CORE PHILOSOPHY
==================================================

Contracts tell users:
“What opportunities exist?”

Award history tells users:
“What ACTUALLY wins.”

The platform should prioritize:
real procurement intelligence
over
simple opportunity visibility.

